### Vínculo API - Request Examples
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### ========================================
### DONATIONS
### ========================================

### Create a new donation (individual)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "donor": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "contact": "john@example.com",
    "type": "INDIVIDUAL"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{$guid}}",
      "quantity": 50.0,
      "unit": "KG"
    }
  ]
}

### Create a donation from a company
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "donor": {
    "name": "Food Bank Porto",
    "contact": "contact@foodbank.pt",
    "type": "COMPANY"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{$guid}}",
      "quantity": 100.0,
      "unit": "KG"
    },
    {
      "productId": "{{$guid}}",
      "quantity": 50.0,
      "unit": "LITER",
      "expiryDate": "2027-06-01"
    }
  ]
}

### Create anonymous donation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "donor": {
    "type": "INDIVIDUAL"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{$guid}}",
      "quantity": 25.0,
      "unit": "UNIT"
    }
  ]
}

### Accept a donation (requires warehouseId)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donations/{{donationId}}/accept?warehouseId={{warehouseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Reject a donation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/donations/{{donationId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

### ========================================
### REQUESTS (Distribution)
### ========================================

### Create distribution request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouseId": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "organization": {
    "name": "NGO Porto",
    "contact": "ngo@porto.pt",
    "zone": "Porto",
    "type": "NGO"
  },
  "deliveryAddress": {
    "address": "123 Porto Street",
    "notes": "Side entrance"
  },
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "quantityRequested": 30.0,
      "unit": "KG"
    }
  ]
}

### Get request status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requests/{{requestId}}

### ========================================
### INVENTORY
### ========================================

### Get warehouse stock
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/warehouses/{{warehouseId}}/stock

### Get warehouse info
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/inventory/warehouses/{{warehouseId}}

### ========================================
### DISASTER
### ========================================

### Create disaster event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/disasters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "FLOOD",
  "location": {
    "address": "Avenida dos Aliados, Porto",
    "latitude": 41.1475,
    "longitude": -8.6158
  }
}

### Assess disaster needs
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/disasters/{{disasterId}}/needs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "affectedArea": "Downtown Porto",
  "severity": "HIGH",
  "needs": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "quantityNeeded": 500.0,
      "priority": "CRITICAL"
    }
  ]
}

### ========================================
### AUTH
### ========================================

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### ========================================
### SWAGGER UI
### ========================================

# View API documentation
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html

# View OpenAPI spec
GET http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs